        <li>Results may vary based on ingredients and cooking methods</li>
        <li>Consult a healthcare professional for dietary advice</li>
        <li>We are not responsible for allergic reactions or food safety issues</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Fan-Made Project</h2>
      <p>
        K-Drama Kitchen is an independent fan project. We are not affiliated with,
        endorsed by, or sponsored by any drama production companies, networks,
        or streaming services.
      </p>
      <p>
        All K-Drama titles, character names, and related content are the property
        of their respective owners. References are made under fair use for
        commentary and educational purposes.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>
        Our site may contain links to external websites. We are not responsible
        for the content or practices of these sites.
      </p>

      <h2>Advertisements</h2>
      <p>
        This site displays advertisements through Google AdSense.
        Ad content is managed by Google and may be personalized based
        on your browsing activity.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time.
        Continued use of the site constitutes acceptance of updated terms.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about these terms? Contact us at
        <a href="mailto:re171113@gmail.com">re171113@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-container {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 80px 24px;
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    padding-bottom: 32px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .updated {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }

  .page-content .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .page-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 40px 0 16px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .page-content p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .page-content ul {
    margin: 16px 0 24px;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .page-content li {
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .page-content li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .page-content a {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .page-content a:hover {
    text-decoration-thickness: 2px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-container {
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }

    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }

    .page-content .lead {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
